18
00:00:30,036 --> 00:00:31,563
violence and making retreat

19
00:00:31,563 --> 00:00:32,509
impossible.

20
00:00:32,728 --> 00:00:34,546
Rome panicked, and military loyalty

21
00:00:34,546 --> 00:00:35,928
